709146f-a.title: Manhattan: 5th Avenue - 77th Street
709146f-a.text:
(1)
960 to 968 Fifth Ave., east side, north from East 77th to but not
including 78th Street, showing the demolition of Nos. 960 and 963, at and
adjoining the N.E. corner of East 77th Street. The two remaining houses
are Nos. 964 and 968; the latter being the Jacob H. Schiff home. No. 960,
the former corner building was the home of Senator Wm. A. Clark of
Nevada. This with the adjoining building, No. 963 form the site of the
present large apartment house; built by Anthony Campagna.
August 30, 1927.
L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
No. 968 Fifth Ave.; the Jacob H. Schiff home.
July 21, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
No REPRODUCTIONS.
